properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 20 at 11:37AM MST until February 20 at 8:00PM MST by NWS El Paso TX/Santa Teresa NM
properties.description:
* WHAT...East winds 25 to 30 mph with gusts up to 40 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Portions of El Paso and Dona Ana Counties immediately
west of the Franklin and Organ Mountains. This includes the I-
10 corridor between the west side of El Paso and Las Cruces.

* WHEN...Through 8 PM MST this evening.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...A strong backdoor cold front will bring
strong easterly winds to the region. Cross winds will develop
along Interstate 10 between west El Paso and Las Cruces.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 8 PM MST THIS EVENING
